comment._content:
@rocketpad: thanks so much for taking the effort to figure this all out. If only I still lived in Yokohama, I'd gladly go and take that photo. I actually lived not far from that park, although I don't believe I ever came across this particular park, or realized any significance of it.

The name Maeda-bashi rings no bells. But it does show up as a still-extant placename on Google Maps. ... Looking at it on Street View, I realize I've crossed that bridge countless times while living there, just never realized the name of the bridge.

Very very neat. Thanks again for the info!
